{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b6a9c3d24f","title":"周恩来给纪登奎汪东兴的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"15c25dbc0a","index":0,"year":1972,"month":12,"day":18,"articleId":"b6a9c3d24f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3c11982f62","name":"汪东兴","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"9a50528209","name":"纪登奎","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cbc04bea5b","type":"title","text":"周恩来给纪登奎汪东兴的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b6a9c3d24f"},{"id":"793517a45d","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b6a9c3d24f"},{"id":"d809ae8d4b","type":"paragraph","text":"昨晚主席面示，谭震林同志虽有一时错误（现在看来，当时大闹怀仁堂是林彪故意造成打倒一批老同志的局势所激成的），但还是好同志，应该让他回来。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b6a9c3d24f"},{"id":"c56e48e095","type":"paragraph","text":"此事请你们二人商办，他在桂林摔伤了骨头，曾请韦国清同志注意帮他治好。王良恩同志了解其情况，可问他关于震林同志一家的近情。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b6a9c3d24f"},{"id":"c84d5727a2","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平同志一家曾要求做点工作，请你们也考虑一下，主席也曾提过几次。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b6a9c3d24f"},{"id":"f24c99708b","type":"paragraph","text":" 周恩来一九七二年十二月十八日","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b6a9c3d24f"}],"page":{"id":"1d2a92bc96","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b6a9c3d24f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}